OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,FThe family of a toddler from Wakefield
OL,7,Fwho has an incredibly rare genetic
OL,8,Fcondition say moving their life to the
OL,9,FUS so he can get pioneering treatment
OL,10,Fis the "only chance" they have to help
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,FSixteen-month-old Eliyas Bashir is
OL,14,Fbelieved to be only one of 12 children
OL,15,Fin the world with a rare form of
OL,16,FLeukodystrophy which affects the
OL,17,Fdevelopment of his brain and body
OL,18,Fmovement.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,FHis parents noticed something was
OL,7,Fwrong when he was failing to hit
OL,8,Fmilestones such as holding up his own
OL,9,Fhead as a baby.
OL,11,FNow at sixteen months old, he has the
OL,12,Fgross motor skills - movements
OL,13,Finvolving the body's largest muscles -
OL,14,Fof a three-month-old.
OL,16,FMum Jasmin Matharun said: "(The
OL,17,Fdiagnosis) was an utter shock. Our
OL,18,Fworld completely stopped. It was
OL,19,Falmost like the walls had closed in on
OL,20,Fus.
OL,26,@xD@\pmyD@Jpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,F"As a parent, all you want is for your
OL,7,Fchild to be healthy and happy. You
OL,8,Fdon't think they're going to be
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with an ultra rare brain
OL,10,Fcondition. Something so random,
OL,11,Fsomething not inherited.
OL,13,F"His brain and his body are not
OL,14,Fcatching up with each other. So day-to-
OL,15,Fday he's very much still handled like
OL,16,Fa newborn. So it's essentially like
OL,17,Fhaving a newborn for 16 months and we
OL,18,Fhave a lot of physio we have to do day-
OL,19,Fto-day too."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,FThe family has found a pioneering
OL,7,Ftrial being run in Chicago for
OL,8,Fchildren with Eliyas's condition.
OL,10,FBut it means moving to the US so he
OL,11,Fcan take part, which comes at a huge
OL,12,Fcost.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
