FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,FJasmin said: "It's the only chance
OL,7,Fwe've got. We don't have any other
OL,8,Foption. It's genuinely life or death
OL,9,Ffor Elyias. Because currently he's
OL,10,Fstill progressing but by the age of 3
OL,11,Fhe will decline and we only know of
OL,12,Fone child that's made it to the age of
OL,13,F13 at the moment. So we haven't got a
OL,14,Fchoice."
OL,16,FA GoFundMe appeal set up by the family
OL,17,Fhas so far raised over #26,000.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
