PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,FProfessor Elizabeth Berry-Kravis is
OL,7,Frunning the trial at the Rush
OL,8,FUniversity Medical Center in Chicago
OL,9,Fand told ITV News the condition is
OL,10,Fvery rare and Elyias has the early
OL,11,Fonset form.
OL,13,FShe said: "He's very motor delayed, he
OL,14,Fcan look at you and interact and
OL,15,Fcommunicate some but the disease
OL,16,Freally prevents him from making those
OL,17,Fnormal developmental gains that we
OL,18,Ftypically see in a young baby."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,FThe trial Eliyas could join involves
OL,7,Fgene therapy where medication is
OL,8,Fdelivered through a spinal tap.
OL,10,FThe drug can genetically correct the
OL,11,Fcondition, but patients are required
OL,12,Fto be monitored for months before and
OL,13,Fafter being treated.
OL,15,FProf Berry-Kravis: "We see the patient
OL,16,Ffor at least six months and oftentimes
OL,17,Flonger while they're waiting to get
OL,18,Fthe drug.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,F"And we track them in really every
OL,7,Fdevelopmental area so we know at what
OL,8,Frate their speech is developing, at
OL,9,Fwhat rate their fine motor skills with
OL,10,Ftheir hands are developing, at what
OL,11,Frate their gross motor skills like
OL,12,Fwalking or sitting are developing.
OL,14,F"And then we have a trajectory - we
OL,15,Fhave a rate of gain from before the
OL,16,Fpatient gets treatment and then they
OL,17,Fgo on the treatment."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
