CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780683078
OL,3,CToddler is one of only 12 children
OL,4,Cworldwide with rare genetic condition
OL,6,FOnly two patients with the condition
OL,7,Fhave been treated at the Rush Medical
OL,8,FCenter and Prof Berr-Kravis say it's
OL,9,Ftoo early to say how successful it has
OL,10,Fbeen.
OL,12,FShe said: "It's always hard when a
OL,13,Fpatient has developed abnormally for a
OL,14,Fwhile to change the brain and correct
OL,15,Fthe abnormal development. And it takes
OL,16,Fa while to see whether that's going to
OL,17,Fhappen or not."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
